{"id":645097,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/05/usdollar-留学生回不了国，是因为被美国扣为人质了/","date":"2020-05-22T06:12:13Z","modified":"2020-05-22T06:12:13Z","title":"USDollar | 留学生回不了国，是因为“被美国扣为人质”了？","content":"<h3>01、“被美国扣为人质了”！</h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>自从写完《<a href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI0NDkxNjE5Nw==&amp;mid=2247484617&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=737ec758d859a3a5040f0c5756bca71f&amp;chksm=e957ce43de20475538f19c2661887bbc2243d1e28fee11e063522cd7be7a3628ebefb075d1c6&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\">疫情期间，留学生回国的条件是什么</a>》后，我就没再跟踪留学生回国这个话题。</p>\n<p>因为，我想着，大国撤侨开始慢了点也能理解，但这都两个月了，应该已经撤到尾声了吧。</p>\n<p>今天打开微博一看。</p>\n<p>发现，我又天真了。</p>\n<p>原来留学生还是没有回到祖国的怀抱。</p>\n<p>而没有回来的原因，居然是，“被美国扣为人质了”。</p>\n<p>官媒5月20日的原帖如下：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-645099\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质-119x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1264\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质-119x300.jpg 119w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质-405x1024.jpg 405w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质-768x1941.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质-608x1536.jpg 608w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质-810x2048.jpg 810w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质-scaled.jpg 1013w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>如果把上贴当作一道阅读理解的考题，原帖下的评论和转发是两种不同的解读。</p>\n<p><strong>一：先来截屏看一下评论。</strong></p>\n<p>关键词：“扣留人质”，“美国无耻”</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-645100\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质2-183x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"819\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质2-183x300.jpg 183w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质2-625x1024.jpg 625w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质2-768x1259.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质2-937x1536.jpg 937w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质2.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>关键词：“在美留学风险大”，“美国政府没有人道主义精神”。“流氓美国”。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-645101\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质3-8-216x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"693\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质3-8-216x300.jpg 216w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质3-8-739x1024.jpg 739w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质3-8-768x1065.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质3-8.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-645102\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质4-7-217x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"690\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质4-7-217x300.jpg 217w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质4-7-742x1024.jpg 742w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质4-7-768x1060.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质4-7.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>关键词：“留学生是白眼狼”</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-645103\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质5-5-300x237.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"395\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质5-5-300x237.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质5-5-1024x809.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质5-5-768x607.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质5-5.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>二：再来看一下此贴的转发。</strong></p>\n<p>关键词：“中国民航局申请晚了”</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-645104\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质6-1-300x164.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"273\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质6-1-300x164.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质6-1-1024x558.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质6-1-768x419.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质6-1.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-645113\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质15-1-300x142.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"237\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质15-1-300x142.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质15-1-1024x485.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质15-1-768x364.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质15-1.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>关键词：“戏真不错”，“转移矛盾”</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-645105\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质7-1-261x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"575\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质7-1-261x300.jpg 261w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质7-1-891x1024.jpg 891w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质7-1-768x882.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质7-1.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>这评论和转发之间的鸿沟，基本上算是道高考的语文阅读理解题吧？</p>\n<p>这到底在说什么？</p>\n<p>算是为了高考预热，我也试着做了一下这道阅读理解题。答案是，“留学生是不是“人质”不好说，但好像评论里的乡亲们还是不想让他们回来。”</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>02、“跟现男友在一起得了性病又去找前男友治病”</h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>乡亲们为什么还是不想让留学生回国？</p>\n<p>我上次写《<a href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI0NDkxNjE5Nw==&amp;mid=2247484571&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=259f0ee1be0b240928cbce406d783439&amp;chksm=e957ce11de204707d0bfc482665fc78389030ff48d3918d33d75b7b4e01532aae6c2f5637712&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\">哪个瞬间，让你为祖国感到自豪？评论大翻车</a>》试图找到这个答案。</p>\n<p>留言精选一百，开眼开眼再开眼之后，还是在持续地收到不少让人眼前一亮的回答。这里甄选几条没能上精选的乡亲们的想法，让大家试图相互理解一下。</p>\n<p><strong>一.留学生是“跟现男友在一起得了性病又去找前男友治病”。</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-645106\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质8-1-300x136.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"226\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质8-1-300x136.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质8-1-1024x463.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质8-1-768x347.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质8-1.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>二. 留学生都是“王八犊子，回国就折腾普通老百姓”。</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-645107\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质9-3-300x171.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"285\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质9-3-300x171.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质9-3-1024x584.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质9-3-768x438.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质9-3.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>三.留学生是“巨婴”</strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-645108\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质10-1-300x258.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"431\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质10-1-300x258.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质10-1-1024x882.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质10-1-768x661.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质10-1.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<h3>03、继续“五个一”政策</h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>也不管那么多贴在留学生身上的野生标签了。毕竟14亿人嘛，林子大了，啥鸟都有。</p>\n<p>再说了，外交部从4月一直在说，留学生是祖国的孩子。那总归还是要回国的。</p>\n<p>留学生回不回了国，不在于你说了啥，他说了啥，还是在于行动，在于有没有飞机。</p>\n<p>即使“人质”了，提前7天多申请点飞机，也还是能解救出来的。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-645109\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质11-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"198\" /></p>\n<p>翻了一下民航局的政策。</p>\n<p>发现5月19日，民航局刚发了通告。</p>\n<p>关键词：继续“五个一”政策。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-645110\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质12-1-300x222.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"370\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质12-1-300x222.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质12-1-1024x759.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质12-1-768x569.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质12-1.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>在#未复航航空公司不得提前预售国际机票# 这个tag下，有很多留学生的叙事。如果想看到在“人质”，“巨婴”和“王八犊子”这些标签的背面是什么，可以点开那个tag看一下。</p>\n<p>这里有一篇一个留学生的长文“我不明白为什么”，可以算作各种留学生自述的总结。（我没有找到作者信息，如果有人知道的话，请在留言区标注。）</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-645111\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质13-65x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"2291\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质13-335x1536.jpg 335w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质13.jpg 447w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>读后感也不想说什么了。就用民航网的一条微博结束吧。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-645112\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质14-300x291.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"485\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质14-300x291.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质14-768x745.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质14-50x50.jpg 50w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/人质14.jpg 1021w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":1067,"categories":[18271,38912,38960,38919],"tags":[24447,40609,10270,40339]}